## Quality Checklist

### Content Funnel Review Checklist
- [ ] Funnel stages are clearly defined and optimized
- [ ] Content supports each stage's conversion goals
- [ ] Value propositions are clear and compelling
- [ ] CTAs are prominent and action-oriented
- [ ] Personalization is implemented where appropriate
- [ ] A/B testing is planned and executed
- [ ] Metrics are tracked and analyzed
- [ ] Content quality is consistent across all stages
- [ ] User experience is smooth and intuitive
- [ ] Conversion rates are optimized and improving
